after a speech thursday in which he denounced israel, lauded the palestine liberation organization and blasted congress and the reagan administration, ambassador clovis maksoud was invited to state his preference in the presidential sweepstakes
well, i don't want to say who's the preferred presidential candidate, because that almost would be the kiss of death, so i would suggest _ i would suggest pat robertson,'' maksoud said, provoking laughter from the audience
