we elected 45 robertson supporters ... and we have 20 sympathizers on the committee already so we feel we have close to 65 of the 140 votes from the start,'' said john rodeno, a coordinator for robertson's campaign
robertson's near majority on the central committee was the result of a well-orchestrated strategy. prompted by a direct mail and telephone campaign, robertson forces made a point of marking ballots for state central committee posts during last week's super tuesday primaries
most of louisiana's other republican voters chose only presidential candidates at the polls that day
