takeover news and rumors continued at their recent frenetic pace
firestone tire &amp; rubber jumped 15\ to 77} in active trading. the company agreed thursday to be acquired by bridgestone of japan for $80 a share, in a deal that topped a previous $58-a-share bid by pirelli group of italy
roper corp. climbed 5} to 53. whirlpool corp. raised its offer for roper to $50 a share, surpassing a $45-a-share bid by general electric
